org.ezze.games.storekeeper.Game.WorkerDirection workerDirection
Stores worker's current glance direction.

workerDeltaX

int workerDeltaX
Stores worker's desired horizontal shift forced by user. Can be equal to -1, 0, 1.

workerDeltaY

int workerDeltaY
Stores worker's desired vertical shift forced by user. Can be equal to -1, 0, 1.

isWorkerIdle

boolean isWorkerIdle
Shows whether worker is idle right now.

isAnimationInProgress

boolean isAnimationInProgress
Shows whether animation is in progress.

workerAnimPhase

int workerAnimPhase
Worker's animation phase's index. This index must no less than 0 and less than GameGraphics.getActionSpritesCount() of Game.gameGraphics. Animation phase with index 0 corresponds to idle worker while another ones represent worker's motion.

workerAnimDestX

int workerAnimDestX
Keeps worker's destination X coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purporses only. This variable is a local copy of the current GameLevel.workerX. Default value -1 means that worker is idle and no animation is in progress.

workerAnimDestY

int workerAnimDestY
Keeps worker's destination Y coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purporses only. This variable is a local copy of the current GameLevel.workerY. Default value -1 means that worker is idle and no animation is in progress.

workerAnimCurrX

double workerAnimCurrX
Keeps worker's current X animation coordinate of GameLevel field. Please note that this variable is used for animation purporses only while X coordinate GameLevel.workerX of worker's real position is always integer.

workerAnimCurrY

double workerAnimCurrY
Keeps worker's current Y animation coordinate of GameLevel field. Please note that this variable is used for animation purporses only while Y coordinate GameLevel.workerY of worker's real position is always integer.

workerAnimDeltaX

double workerAnimDeltaX
Worker's X animation shift to be performed during current loop execution. This one is determined as GameGraphics.getAnimationStepShift() of Game.gameGraphics for each horizontal worker's animation. Animation continues until Game.workerAnimCurrX reaches Game.workerAnimDestX and Game.workerAnimCurrY reaches Game.workerAnimDestY.

workerAnimDeltaY

double workerAnimDeltaY
Worker's Y animation shift to be performed during current loop execution. This one is determined as GameGraphics.getAnimationStepShift() of Game.gameGraphics for each vertical worker's animation. Animation continues until Game.workerAnimCurrX reaches Game.workerAnimDestX and Game.workerAnimCurrY reaches Game.workerAnimDestY.

boxAnimDestX

int boxAnimDestX
Keeps moving box' destination X coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purposes only. This one is similar to Game.workerAnimDestX but relative to moving box.

boxAnimDestY

int boxAnimDestY
Keeps moving box' destination Y coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purporses only. This one is similar to Game.workerAnimDestY but relative to moving box.

boxAnimCurrX

double boxAnimCurrX
Keeps moving box' current X animation coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purporses only. This one is similar to Game.workerAnimCurrX but relative to moving box.

boxAnimCurrY

double boxAnimCurrY
Keeps moving box' current Y animation coordinate of GameLevel field and is used for animation purporses only. This one is similar to Game.workerAnimCurrY but relative to moving box.

boxAnimDeltaX

double boxAnimDeltaX
Moving box' X shift to be performed during current loop execution. This one is equal to zero or to Game.workerAnimDeltaX due to box' shift can be caused only by similar worker's movement.

boxAnimDeltaY

double boxAnimDeltaY
Moving box' Y shift to be performed during current loop execution. This one is equal to zero or to Game.workerAnimDeltaY due to box' shift can be caused only by similar worker's movement.
